name: Aphrodite Pandemos
description:
"A story about the world? Yes yes, we know one"
This is how the journey of the artists to show their vision about the Greek gods and their forms begin.

#cryptoamigues #CryptOlimpianos

My Brazilian version of Aphrodite's epithet, mounted on a Collared peccary (Cateto/Caititu) and together with the parrot cupids. She spreads love and respect to all kinds of differences, to all peoples. It helps to live in peace with all humanity, to live with differences and respect them.
